parts.content:
The `ultralytics/models/sam/modules/decoders.py` file in the Ultralytics repository primarily defines and implements the `MaskDecoder` and `SAM2MaskDecoder` modules. These modules are crucial for efficient mask prediction within the SAM (Segment Anything Model) and SAM2 architectures, utilizing a transformer-based design.

Reference: [ultralytics-main/docs/en/reference/models/sam/modules/decoders.md](https://github.com/ultralytics/ultralytics/blob/main/ultralytics-main/docs/en/reference/models/sam/modules/decoders.md)
